  "detailed_description": "<h1>Instructions</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. You can play alone at night, but it is recommended to play with roommates or friends. If it happens to be a friend's birthday, you can send him directly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. Tips: This game is not scary, but it can help raise blood pressure and greatly reduce the risk of blood vessel blockage. Unique groups of people can have a sleep aid.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. You can contact us through the contact information below</p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/1c342cffb02bd9639983d93d05e2e6d3.avif?t=1732711329\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Background of the Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Peach and Lee\" Village is a village in the mountains, 20 minutes drive from the town, there are some planting bases in its vicinity, and some of the staff will rent a room in the village for temporary residence for the sake of convenience. The village is very harmonious, everyone knows each other. In October of that year, the protagonist of the university received a phone call from Auntie Liu, who learned that her mother was seriously ill and returned to visit her hometown, and thus the story begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/62e66753e39016bb3b972163fa489d38.avif?t=1732711329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras_big/62e66753e39016bb3b972163fa489d38.avif?t=1732711329 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Way of Playing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore this familiar and unfamiliar village from a first-person perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn the origins and reasons behind this layout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/d0b073559ed6905a513fa606e3feb754.poster.avif?t=1732711329\" width=800 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/d0b073559ed6905a513fa606e3feb754.webm?t=1732711329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/d0b073559ed6905a513fa606e3feb754.mp4?t=1732711329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story is divided into a bright line and a dark line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The bright line is the main plot and reveals the cause of the anomaly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dark storyline is interspersed with the main storyline and involves exploring the village to find the original cause.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partially open map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/f23cf643080687759c3d836eb39fc017.avif?t=1732711329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras_big/f23cf643080687759c3d836eb39fc017.avif?t=1732711329 width=800 height=396 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is for the joyful times when you used to play horror games with your housemates, may you cherish them.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >               <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/1c342cffb02bd9639983d93d05e2e6d3.avif?t=1732711329\" width=462 height=174 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Background of the Story</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Peach and Lee\" Village is a village in the mountains, 20 minutes drive from the town, there are some planting bases in its vicinity, and some of the staff will rent a room in the village for temporary residence for the sake of convenience. The village is very harmonious, everyone knows each other. In October of that year, the protagonist of the university received a phone call from Auntie Liu, who learned that her mother was seriously ill and returned to visit her hometown, and thus the story begins.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/62e66753e39016bb3b972163fa489d38.avif?t=1732711329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras_big/62e66753e39016bb3b972163fa489d38.avif?t=1732711329 width=800 height=400 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Way of Playing</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore this familiar and unfamiliar village from a first-person perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn the origins and reasons behind this layout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/d0b073559ed6905a513fa606e3feb754.poster.avif?t=1732711329\" width=800 height=428 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/d0b073559ed6905a513fa606e3feb754.webm?t=1732711329\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/d0b073559ed6905a513fa606e3feb754.mp4?t=1732711329\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story is divided into a bright line and a dark line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The bright line is the main plot and reveals the cause of the anomaly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The dark storyline is interspersed with the main storyline and involves exploring the village to find the original cause.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Partially open map.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras/f23cf643080687759c3d836eb39fc017.avif?t=1732711329\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3235580/extras_big/f23cf643080687759c3d836eb39fc017.avif?t=1732711329 width=800 height=396 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is for the joyful times when you used to play horror games with your housemates, may you cherish them.</p>",
